      <p class="tldr__body" id="kitchen-sink-e5-tool-tldr-body">TechBrot&rsquo;s tool pages each run one small in-browser island and then hand off to a person. The bookkeeping cost calculator estimates a <strong>$400&ndash;$2,500+/month</strong> fixed-fee range from five factors; the budget worksheet does plain math on your own numbers; the QuickBooks plan selector recommends a tier on feature fit, never price. Some questions &mdash; like an exact sales tax rate &mdash; are deliberately call-based, because a wrong number is worse than no number. Every island is an estimate or starting point, not a quote or advice; the real answer is confirmed in writing on a free discovery call.</p>
